e events, but with much tighter uncertainty bounds, and which\ncan be extended to events of unprecedented severity that have not yet been\nobserved historically. These methods hold potential for assessing extreme\nevents throughout the climate system, beyond this example of stratospheric\nextremes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Jun 2022 21:38:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2023 03:19:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-25"}
