ar magnetic fields and to\nimprove theoretical models. The method developed to reveal the spurious signals\ncan be applied to each of the released Gaia photometric time-series and can be\nexploited by anyone interested in working directly with Gaia time-series.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Jun 2022 11:06:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2022 13:53:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
